<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-11-07T16:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-11-07T16:00:00-05:00" n="400" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d400">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72119/2542a</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                    to the Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_SWG1" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Sharp</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-11-07T16:00:00-05:00">
                                        <hi rend="italic">November 7, 1918, 4 p.m.</hi>
                                    </date>
                                </dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>6198. United Press received telegram today before 1 p.m. announcing
                                armistice had been signed. Telegram published at once and greatest
                                excitement and enthusiasm prevails. This Department and War
                                Department have been informed no foundation for story. Please find
                                out why censor passed this report as the incident is most
                                unfortunate.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>